{"tid":119954,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"拍東京喰種「吃人肉」情節違背良心 清水富美加出家幸福科學原因曝光","createTime":"2017-02-14T06:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T16:04:27.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d6d0cdcce63a43c73d520bc1b0ebf4e6c96262f","tid":119954,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:35:19.000Z","msg":"22歲日本女星清水富美加12日宣布出家，投身新興宗教「幸福科學」，閃退演藝圈投下震撼彈。原本2017年主演的3部電影將陸續上映，如今她所有的演出工作全部暫停，教團更透露她因為接演「吃人肉的角色」，心情陷入低潮，令真人版電影《東京喰種》陷入上映危機。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2329/d2329714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2329%2Fd2329714.jpg&h=0354bbc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清水富美加擔任《東京喰種》的女主角「霧島董香」，為此剪掉30公分長髮，該作品改編自超人氣漫畫，描述吃人肉的「喰種」隱藏在大都會中，窪田正孝扮演被半人半喰種的大學生，兩人有眾多精采對手戲。據「幸福科學」教團透露，她因為演出吃人肉的角色，違背良心和思想信念，因為害怕被經紀公司冷凍，不敢拒絕戲約，身處在痛苦的工作環境中，經過醫生診斷，認為需要靜養，所以中斷所有表演工作。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2330/d2330293.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2330%2Fd2330293.jpg&h=3a6c9b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲清水富美加因為演吃人肉感到很痛苦：「違背良心和信念。」<br />\n<br />\n《東京喰種》原作擁有高評價，開拍真人版時，曾引發動漫迷抗議，網友憂心演員陣容，以及特效表現。對此原作者石田翠曾在寫下暖文稱讚拍攝團隊，「都是很優秀的演員。」沒想到女主角清水富美加竟吐露抗拒心情，令大批粉絲擔心會影響電影上映。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2330/d2330294.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2330%2Fd2330294.jpg&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e693fcda\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2330/d2330294.jpg</a><br />\n▲清水富美加揭露被逼拍泳裝寫真。<br />\n<br />\n決定出家的清水富美加，親筆信同時接露了經紀公司的低薪、奴隸契約，被逼拍泳裝寫真等，引起外界高度關注。除了7月的《東京喰種》，她4月有2部電影《黑暗女子》、《招笑貓》率先上映，配合宣傳的可能性極低，經紀公司則希望她能在合約期間內完成工作。"},{"pid":"36ea833f9af9a41837234ba4e922cc096a7de4de","tid":119954,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e31e38d9a5f018f16443122eb3e77a6c8c92685","tid":119954,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795ff53c86602758373c08a1074a0976f2fb4dd4","tid":119954,"uid":19301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"真實版金木研內心掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f0b308bf977d0e12d88c3c44538c3ad86643d6","tid":119954,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司vs邪教纏身<br />\n邊樣都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8607aab9e7bd514a59c5aa9dd8e0591217e90753","tid":119954,"uid":70763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"乜鬼教黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414fcf8909a033f0b6dc3d4d328db4eb2800efef","tid":119954,"uid":68394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 似邪教藉口多d"},{"pid":"f8af44084a8520bbb7ead01e862327f495943fd5","tid":119954,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"邪教藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eeb8fef6cedc55e5a3e08fa254b6224c71a3734","tid":119954,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:24:46.000Z","msg":"22歲個樣咁老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73091a5d530814eb6845fbb2780b097edbf33095","tid":119954,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"邊個做金木？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪拍到佢變身個度？個度好經典，好正"},{"pid":"d53c81cbadd1c0b1f7eee3ef07c67f485be28f52","tid":119954,"uid":49056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"高手<br />\n完美咁宣傳左個教<br />\n一大堆人應該聽都未聽過"},{"pid":"b78b8f87d75ae3c09e9a7749676519ea6b71541d","tid":119954,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"google吓清水間公司咩料子再講<br />\nKeywords: 結衣BB, 能年玲奈, 黑社會"},{"pid":"bc4b927c50806851ab72763ec8858eb8f5fd3967","tid":119954,"uid":31229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"902f4f6adcd9166b947c4fed46ae3c14235f4f07","tid":119954,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:31:52.000Z","msg":"串謀被出家迫人違背良心就真"},{"pid":"274e9b0390ec26680b6811340fed1d9f9d599c64","tid":119954,"uid":39630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"個邪教同佢間經理公司都係一擔擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd4e1f6656a0e09056fbc7b4df49986c5bd19fb","tid":119954,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>google吓清水間公司咩料子再講<br />\nKeywords: 結衣BB, 能年玲奈, 黑社會</blockquote><br />\n啱啱search 咗<br />\n係香港01有講<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/004307_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F004307_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7d6e4c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/004314_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F004314_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3f1e7f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/004321_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F004321_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f98e2acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/004329_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F004329_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d4f6b6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/004337_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F004337_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4555c720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/004343_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F004343_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=82a71b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65c1291cdee083cfcbc9d7a8e30986a12f1ba9b5","tid":119954,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"重點：在2011年演出《幪面超人Fourze》時，富美加以清純學生妹形象大受歡迎，其後於《變態超人》及《模仿犯》等作品中，除了有更深層演繹外也有一些性感鏡頭，隨住她人氣漸升，曝光率也大增。就在大家以為富美加前途無限之際，原來鏡頭後她受盡壓榨，從公開信中指出事務所在她成名後更改了合約，當中最過份是固定的月薪制度，無論她拍幾多戲、接幾多廣告，每月也只有5萬日圓（不足港幣4,000元）薪金，而且有很長時間每日只睡3小時。信中富美加又指：「這8年來都在做着不情願的工作，情緒一直很低落，每天都是極限狀態。」<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2c2e2aaccd7bb75a8ab11ef20d297d6c9ec56b","tid":119954,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"最新消息<br />\n<br />\n據《產經新聞》報導，&ldquo;幸福科學&rdquo;受訪表示，清水富美加&ldquo;並不會引退演藝圈&rdquo;，目前她正在調理身體、累積宗教休養，之后會考慮演出以宗教、人道為主題的電影，繼續演藝事業。至于既定的電影宣傳行程，教團發言人則指出，清水目前身心不適合在銀幕前工作，因此絕對無法參加未來的宣傳工作。<br />\n<br />\n此外，有傳富美加的父親欠債5000萬日圓（約200萬令吉），並由宗教團體代還，未知是否與富美加引退有關。至于富美加入行初期所拍的水著DVD及寫真集，近